Session Scope: My Shop (myshop)

  Current Scope:     default
  Session Key:       agent:myshop:default

This session key prevents the agent from accessing other project contexts.
Each project scope gets isolated workspace memory and routing.

Usage:
  docket scope myshop set <project-key>    # Change project scope
  docket scope myshop reset                # Reset to 'default'

